        "Dr. Stephen Vincent Strange",
        "Dr. Stephen Strange, M.D.,[26] a.k.a. Doctor Strange, was the Sorcerer Supreme for Earth-616.[14] Strange was once a brilliant but arrogant Neurosurgeon, until a car accident crippled his hands.[11] When modern medicine failed him, he embarked on a journey to Kamar-Taj in Tibet, where he was trained by the Ancient One.[11] He healed his hands and learned more about Magic, eventually becoming a Master of the Mystic Arts.[14] He settled in the Sanctum Sanctorum in Greenwich Village, New York City, becoming the Earth's protector from any mystical threats.",
